**Himalayas**
Himalayas Jobs is a remote job platform that connects professionals with companies offering fully remote roles across tech, marketing, design, and other fields.
It aggregates and verifies job listings from company career pages and direct postings, ensuring roles are legitimate and genuinely remote.
The platform also provides filters by skills, salary, timezone, and job type, along with personalized recommendations to help users find relevant opportunities efficiently.

Link: https://himalayas.app/jobs
